# Sample Styled Document

This document demonstrates the **Styled Markdown** format used by SDocs.

## Format

Styles are stored as YAML front matter using the `styles` key — the same standard used by Jekyll, Hugo, Obsidian, and Gatsby.

> Drop this file back onto SDocs to restore both content and styles automatically.

## Code example

```js
const { meta, body } = parseFrontMatter(text);
console.log(meta.styles.fontFamily); // "Inter"
```

Done.
